Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.04,0:01:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:21.07,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(320,320)}紡紗曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不明白是不是看錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥怎麼可能會在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.49,0:02:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 跟你說這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 剛才的話對大家可以保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.82,0:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶消失不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該已經把思念波傳給元老院了的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.31,0:03:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是遇到銀的妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去讓這傢伙安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間內隨你怎麼鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是隨我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 怎樣都可以 隨你喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國 德國
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待妳的禮物哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去德國的哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢堡 不來梅 柏林 慕尼黑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國什麼最有名來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汽車？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.98,0:03:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足球不是很厲害嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳到底是去看什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥本連茲國防技術博物館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那方面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.37,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算工資不多 也要去玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有好好的幹事務所的活嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上那個很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反覆要播好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是町長命令嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的狗一直都在對著叫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽抱怨是蒼的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 今天去嗎？卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那曲子記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是唱這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都快要記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.93,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起悠閒的來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 去 才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？練習對手？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 難得的休息日被叫去做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓恭助來做不就可以了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合同裡可是有這款的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 那就明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我漲工資啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.77,0:04:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一(eins) 二(zwei) 三(drei) (德語 怨念)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像話 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒資格說！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.24,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些不像話的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『棒』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『球球球』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.37,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉和姬勢均力敵呢	
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她癡迷武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.42,0:05:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈這來了 彈這來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈到這邊來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 胸大更容易累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.24,0:05:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸小的傢伙是不會理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『手裡劍』
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來差不多是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機票
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有機可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分出勝負了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機票？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝飾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.40,0:06:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡娘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種設定不需要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的 我的德國旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋不住的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 做過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.15,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是失去理智 才是最危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.03,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 好像是我把機票弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.95,0:08:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.90,0:08:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉小姐本來不是妖怪的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小的時候因作亂的妖怪而被侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成了一半人類一半妖怪的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大多人被侵蝕以後會失去自我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然也會有保持清醒的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.23,0:08:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為那傢伙很堅強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『樹』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在變稀薄呢  『七鄉』
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我討厭被約束啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了就好了 贏了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉OK大會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優勝獎品德國旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳相信命運的紅線嗎？相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好偶然哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然？不對 這是必然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是言葉的話 我覺得肯定會勝的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前有要做的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}補習參加者 \N五十音言葉\N以上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.69,0:10:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的專長是德語啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不明白英文 也不會困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}在校門口等妳哦\N卡拉OK的預約已經辦好了\N立即開始特訓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有年輪蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有德國香腸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能喝啤酒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs20}這三樣都是德國的名物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有名嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想獲勝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.41,0:10:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是言葉的話 肯定會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…是認識的吧 和那個半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加工橡膠 樹脂類 酸化亞鉛以及其他的物質\N將這些物質提煉而成為一種具有粘性物質\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:11:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均的伸展在布料上製成 在正中央依附上紗布\N單手也可以進行治療的醫療物品…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.77,0:11:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 但是普通說聲『OK繃』 出不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.98,0:11:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像牆壁 冰之類的簡單物質可以直接顯現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言靈也不是萬能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是蠻不便的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？那個孩子就是半妖啊 ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.84,0:11:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意外的普通吶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像人類一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼名字來著…那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要邊唱歌邊練習啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要在卡拉OK大會上取得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然天空的有著很高的距離感(町歌)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是朝向遼闊的空中…飛去吧(町歌)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.10,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這首歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.14,0:12:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蹭蹭 得累 蹭得累 蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道她們先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那位半妖小姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（不曉得的他在唱蝦米東東）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 那個是什麼啊 歌曲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌曲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是朗讀一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像說唱一樣不是很帥氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道言葉去哪裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到了仍然沒有到事務所來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙偷懶去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也打過電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可能是在練習卡拉OK的歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個傢伙也是…那個傢伙也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有把我也給加進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.16,0:13:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接通了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.33,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 現在有要事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.05,0:13:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的可真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掛斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個男人的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心…沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.86,0:13:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向她們打聽到了許多關於妳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直在哭鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就讓她們稍微的睡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然對我的朋友出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是向她們打聽了一點事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.64,0:14:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『棒』
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們非要相互爭鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同為被侵蝕之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,侵蝕？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和妳都是被妖怪選中的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.92,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『手榴彈』
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是強勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是正是因為這種力量而被人類所討厭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.41,0:16:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也應該是明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪和人類是不肯能在一起生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『斧頭 斧頭 斧頭 斧頭 斧頭…』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強自己阿諛奉承 裝作和一般人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.59,0:16:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人類卻不把妳當作同類 討厭妳 憎恨妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳今後依舊也要生活在這種世界中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.64,0:16:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.72,0:16:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是一座偽善的城鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說 這個世界是痛苦的 難道不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就讓我們來製造原本屬於我們的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:16:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不知道那種理論
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照自己的想法去做就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墜落之時的妖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不屬於人類 是和我們一樣的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對…不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 不要忘記那天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是隔壁班的五十音言葉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.67,0:18:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是人類 名字是言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了那麼簡單的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 那個就是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳還真是會給我添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…正在興頭上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是円神的手下？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就來作為妳的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.75,0:18:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『彈彈彈彈彈彈…』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.73,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.33,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.31,0:19:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在全力戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個去練歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都預約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.33,0:20:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要取得優勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡唱歌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個就可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:41.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音…聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲……聲音啞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是我會贏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.07,0:20:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不肯能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 德國
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的德國啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.39,0:22:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}幹勁十足的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:33.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出錢來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.78,0:22:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉好厲害 能幹的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被欺騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.78,0:22:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拆穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便浪費言靈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}戰鬥中的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『Maschinenpistole(衝鋒鎗)』
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.99,0:22:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能幹 真能幹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  加油  言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不頂用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}學習中的女子高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.33,0:23:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫習書本
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正安時代（正安 日本鐮倉末期的年號）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.22,0:23:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約至今1250年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言葉看上去好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.32,0:23:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨近考試了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖德太子 聖德太子跑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.89,0:23:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓他回去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提問 我會變出什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑十毫米圓型的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將石灰 石鹼和炭酸鈉經高溫融化做成的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.81,0:23:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又或者使用合成樹脂…
